title: Post With Code
text:
This is a post with executable code.



import databento as db

db.enable_logging("INFO")

symbols = ["GS    251219C00850000",]

live_client = db.Live("db-La5MiWdqshV8EqAmLHHkvC3DbcbH6")

live_client.subscribe(
    dataset = "OPRA.PILLAR",
    schema = "status",
    symbols = symbols,
    stype_in = "raw_symbol",
)

live_client.subscribe(
    dataset = "OPRA.PILLAR",
    schema = "tcbbo",
    symbols = symbols,
    stype_in = "raw_symbol",
)

live_client.subscribe(
    dataset = "OPRA.PILLAR",
    schema = "statistics",
    symbols = symbols,
    stype_in = "raw_symbol",
)

live_client.add_callback(print)
live_client.start()
